<p><img src="http://www.edenhrconsulting.com/images/stories/eden-stick-figures/eden-dismissal.jpg" alt="eden-dismissal" style="float: right;" height="268" width="300" />The term 'dismissal' covers the whole gammit of reasons why employees leave an organisation. For whatever reason employees are being dismissed from their employment, the Organisation is statistically at it's greatest threat of an employment tribunal claim.</p>
<p>At Eden HR Consulting we try not to unduly focus on the possibility of tribunal claims, however, dismissals are the most contentious issues between employer and employee, and claims for unfair dismissal are the largest proportion of claims at tribunal.</p>
<p>Eden HR Consulting can guide you through the process, manage and minimise risk to the Organisation. We can do everything from dealing with simply advising to dealing with an issue in its entirety; such as gross misconduct, performance issues, absenteeism and the like.  We can assist with writing documentation and letters though to conducting meetings on the Organisations behalf.  Please contact us to find out how we can assist you<a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=93&amp;Itemid=216">.</a></p>
